ll, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1002898, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Glory be to He who watches over, never leaves anything undone, or is neglectful. Glory be to He who is Merciful, never does a thing in haste. Glory be to He who is vigilant, never forgets one thing over another. Glory be to He who is alert and steady, never is engrossed with a thing so as to overlook another.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ba-Barkat hai Uski zaat jo hifaazat karne waala aur kabhi ghaflat nahi karta. Ba-Barkat hai Uski zaat jo raheem hai aur jo ujlat (jaldi) nahi karta. Ba-barkat hai woh zaat jo hamesha bar-qaraar rehne waala hai aur woh kabhi bhulta nahi. Ba-barkat hai woh zaat jo hamesha rehne waala hai, kabhi Woh be-kaar kaam nahi karta.", "Urdu": "پاک تر ہے وہ خدا جو ایسا نگہبان ہےکہ غافل نہیں ہوتا، پاک تر ہے وہ مہربان جو جلدی نہیں کرتا پاک تر ہے وہ قائم جو کبھی بھولتا نہیں پاک تر ہے وہ ہمیشہ رہنے والا جو کھیل میں نہیں پڑتا۔", "RArabic": "SUBHAANA MAN HOWA HAFEEZOON LAA YAGHFOLO. SUBHAANA MAN HOWA RAHEEMOON LAA YA’JALO. SUBHAANA MAN HOWA QAAEMOON LAA YASHU. SUBHAANA MAN HOWA DAAEMOON LA YALHU.", "ArabicText1": "سُبْحَانَ مَنْ ھُوَ حَفِیْظٌ لَا یَغْفُلُ۔ سُبْحَانَ مَنْ ھُوَ رَحِیْمٌ لَا یَعْجَلُ۔ سُبْحَانَ مَنْ ھُوَقَآئِمٌ لَا یَسْھُوْ۔ سُبْحَانَ مَنْ ھُوَ دَآئِمٌ لَا یَلْھُوْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "Arabic